{"tid":1305151,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"討論下 藍絲打下應對方法","createTime":"2019-07-10T19:33:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T19:58:56.000Z","uid":188374,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bf47caa62ef9f38fa7f72b74a6b716915cb67ce5","tid":1305151,"uid":188374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T19:33:46.000Z","msg":"見到個肥西藍絲打人個頭 <br />\n同埋另一條友比狗拉走係度笑<br />\n嬲撚到仆街 報警又冇用<br />\n希望起底之後叫議員報案 落埋案再跟進<br />\n如果都冇用 我地係要還手<br />\n有狗係度就冇計啦<br />\n如果好似肥西果條片冇狗<br />\n我地拍片還手 唔知會唔會有事？<br />\n如果唔拍打佢 又怕有路人拍片放上網<br />\n得一個方法係帶口罩開拖<br />\n之後搶佢銀包拎佢身份證直接起底<br />\n不過如果我在場 d人唔跟我 我怕唔夠佢做<br />\n香港人好善良 真係怕有人唔跟<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6CJxQkY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6CJxQkY.png&h=274cb864&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7a5d2ad6f42abc95c5fb3544b61860e7877e7a96","tid":1305151,"uid":188374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T19:36:04.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"5531bceb30f5bd3a8150b5bf35155027af4c7987","tid":1305151,"uid":185092,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T19:37:26.000Z","msg":"而家報警都冇用<br />\n大家仲唔還拖等幾時 洗唔洗俾人打死先反抗"},{"pid":"51cebafc03f2d17bfb7af351dda615a55abcf28a","tid":1305151,"uid":99883,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T19:38:08.000Z","msg":"自衛唔犯法，你唔還手都好，擋下都得啦，乜都唔做仲要企上前任人打，根本弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />定係練左鐵布衫呀？<br />\n<br />\n在公眾地方打鬥: 根據第245章《公安條例》第25條，任何人在公眾地方參與非法打鬥即屬犯罪，可被罰款港元5000及監禁12個月。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如打鬥出於自衞，則不屬違法</span></span>。若引用這條例起訴，撿控官須證明該非法打鬥是發生在公眾地方。與其他較輕微的侵害人身罪行一樣，被檢控的人可考慮和爭取其他免起訴的安排。"},{"pid":"bde2572c654d2d67878998e1c83d8cc7a6ed7289","tid":1305151,"uid":188374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T19:41:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c4d85a85f1ff7b570189261ed38779ab72b4ae1","tid":1305151,"uid":102535,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T19:42:39.000Z","msg":"如果被人打個個可以<span style=\"color: red;\">行使自衛權</span><br />\n意思即係如果你實際上認為自己有危險(被打 / 被推撞)已可使用武力<br />\n但必需使用與對方<span style=\"color: red;\">同等或次一級</span>嘅武力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n例如 拳頭交(<span style=\"color: red;\">平級</span>) / 捉住對方雙手(<span style=\"color: red;\">低一級</span>)<br />\n<br />\n如果被人打嗰個唔係你 你驚既可以用次一級(即係捉住手腳)嘅武力制服打人嗰個<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一定要令佢地知驚!!!<br />\n以武制暴<br />\n打必還手</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1305102/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1305102/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"80526f459845813283d5ffc9ccf62f29e84ca600","tid":1305151,"uid":188374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c4d85a85f1ff7b570189261ed38779ab72b4ae1","tid":1305151,"uid":102535,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T19:42:39.000Z","msg":"如果被人打個個可以<span style=\"color: red;\">行使自衛權</span><br />\n意思即係如果你實際上認為自己有危險(被打 / 被推撞)已可使用武力<br />\n但必需使用與對方<span style=\"color: red;\">同等或次一級</span>嘅武力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n例如 拳頭交(<span style=\"color: red;\">平級</span>) / 捉住對方雙手(<span style=\"color: red;\">低一級</span>)<br />\n<br />\n如果被人打嗰個唔係你 你驚既可以用次一級(即係捉住手腳)嘅武力制服打人嗰個<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一定要令佢地知驚!!!<br />\n以武制暴<br />\n打必還手</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1305102/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1305102/page/1</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T19:47:42.000Z","msg":"如果被打果個唔係我<br />\n我幫手捉住佢 我都比佢打埋<br />\n係唔係可以2個人圍佢？"},{"pid":"1f63581ce7dc45a8246ce7f629181b2bc050546e","tid":1305151,"uid":102535,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"80526f459845813283d5ffc9ccf62f29e84ca600","tid":1305151,"uid":188374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c4d85a85f1ff7b570189261ed38779ab72b4ae1","tid":1305151,"uid":102535,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T19:42:39.000Z","msg":"如果被人打個個可以<span style=\"color: red;\">行使自衛權</span><br />\n意思即係如果你實際上認為自己有危險(被打 / 被推撞)已可使用武力<br />\n但必需使用與對方<span style=\"color: red;\">同等或次一級</span>嘅武力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n例如 拳頭交(<span style=\"color: red;\">平級</span>) / 捉住對方雙手(<span style=\"color: red;\">低一級</span>)<br />\n<br />\n如果被人打嗰個唔係你 你驚既可以用次一級(即係捉住手腳)嘅武力制服打人嗰個<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一定要令佢地知驚!!!<br />\n以武制暴<br />\n打必還手</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1305102/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1305102/page/1</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T19:47:42.000Z","msg":"如果被打果個唔係我<br />\n我幫手捉住佢 我都比佢打埋<br />\n係唔係可以2個人圍佢？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T19:58:56.000Z","msg":"有風險 要有片影住個次序<br />\n你幫手制服佢(純粹捉手腳) &gt; 佢襲擊你 &gt;你用同等武力自衛<br />\n最好嘅辦法係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大聲講出嚟</span></span><br />\n「我依家淨係捉住你手腳唔比你再襲擊人」<br />\n「你唔好打埋我，唔係我就自衛還手」<br />\n就算上到法庭<br />\n檢控官係有責任反証自衛的辯護理由不成立<br />\n反証唔到=你係屬於自衛=無罪"}]}